<p>Sup guys just started a new bard on tribunal... came over from bertoxx , have no idea about the strategies of a bard... ive been playing a warrior... could somebody just give me the lowdown on how to play a bard in a group setting as well as a solo scene... also could i get informed on how to twist songs and the use of instruments... thanks&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>
